---
import image from '../assets/image.jpg'
---

<div class="container">
	<img
		class="image"
		src={image.src}
		alt=""
		fetchpriority="high"
		width="385"
		height="427"
	/>
	<h1>Даша Кубик</h1>
	<p>Невероятно красивая девушка и отличный тату мастер</p>
</div>

<style>
	.container {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		min-height: 100vh;
		padding: 60px 20px;
	}

	.image {
		border-radius: 10px;
		margin-bottom: 24px;
		max-width: 100%;
		height: auto;
	}

	h1 {
		margin: 0;
		margin-bottom: 12px;
	}

	p {
		margin: 0;
	}
</style>
